Comment: 10,0:25:53.03,0:25:56.03,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.51,0:03:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.02,0:03:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Karin's pouch?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.32,0:03:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why do you have it, Takamaru?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.03,0:03:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when I woke up this morning, \Nit was by my bedside for some reason.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.68,0:03:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,When you woke up?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.25,0:03:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, where's Karin-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.72,0:03:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.87,0:03:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, \NI haven't seen her today.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.74,0:03:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Karin-san ended up in Champon \Nbecause someone chased her, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.50,0:03:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.22,0:03:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe they finally got her \Nduring this uproar?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.90,0:03:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.90,0:03:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go look for Karin!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.08,0:03:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I also have to report to the castle now.\NPlease look after Mirai for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.72,0:03:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.22,0:03:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.63,0:03:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What did you say?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.11,0:03:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Taro-chan has been turned into stone?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.24,0:04:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugai, Koen, we've gotta help Taro-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.28,0:04:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This could only be the work \Nof that Taiman and his army!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.22,0:04:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please calm down.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.08,0:04:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,To disturb Your Majesty \Nis exactly what the enemy wants.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.23,0:04:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.75,0:04:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's in our best interest \Nto be more on guard now than ever before. {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.26,0:04:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.94,0:04:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugai, Koen! Gather everyone \Nfor a strategy meeting!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.06,0:04:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.45,0:04:25.64,Thought,,0,0,0,,I was so distracted by what happened to Mirai, \NI completely forgot! I'm sorry, Karin.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.22,0:04:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Karin?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.51,0:04:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Al-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.83,0:04:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What, Karin? \NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.65,0:04:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Takamaru-san... \NHe stole Karin's pouch!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.86,0:04:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What did you say?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.52,0:04:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, hold up, are you sure?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.20,0:04:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.07,0:05:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But why'd Takamaru ever need to do that?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.95,0:05:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, actually.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.17,0:05:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai was attacked \Nand seriously injured last night.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.39,0:05:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know anything about it? {replaced kokoro in https://jisho.org/word/%E5%BF%83%E5%BD%93%E3%81%9F%E3%82%8A with heart}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.75,0:05:13.96,Thought,,0,0,0,,Mirai is seriously injured? \NSo then, she didn't die after all?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.96,0:05:14.76,Thought,,0,0,0,,If so...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.76,0:05:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right! \NTakamaru-san did that too!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.51,0:05:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened last night...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.19,0:05:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What could that be?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.82,0:05:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Takamaru-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.77,0:05:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In the flesh! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.34,0:05:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your pouch! Right now!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.68,0:05:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.40,0:05:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been wondering \Nwhat's in there for a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.32,0:05:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been so curious I lost my sleep!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.28,0:05:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So give it to me at once!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.77,0:05:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.21,0:05:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.36,0:05:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.73,0:05:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Takamaru! Breaking into a woman's room \Nlate at night—what's the big idea?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.42,0:06:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It falls on me to punish this pervert boy!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.28,0:06:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{??}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.45,0:06:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Takamaru...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.59,0:06:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Punch!{??}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.14,0:06:07.81,Overlap,,0,0,0,,No way... {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.69,0:06:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see now how strong I truly am?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.41,0:06:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So give me your pouch now \Nand don't make a fuss!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.53,0:06:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.26,0:06:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Surely, that can't be true, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.84,0:06:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't believe what Karin says?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.54,0:06:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No-no, no... I believe it! \NI believe you, so stop crying, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.17,0:06:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry! \NI'll do something about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.65,0:06:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.59,0:06:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Of course!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.10,0:06:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy! \NYou'll fight for me, won't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.15,0:06:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I mean... \NIf I have to... {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.19,0:06:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's the Drill...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.33,0:06:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't fight to the fullest... {because of the dress}{lit: I was immature; inexperienced; unskilled; green}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.88,0:07:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad has turned into stone, \Nand Mirai-san is badly injured!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.50,0:07:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.50,0:07:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro-dono, I understand how you feel, \Nbut boys shouldn't burst into tears that easily.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.69,0:07:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai-dono is gonna laugh at you \Nif she finds out later.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.40,0:07:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Al!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.16,0:07:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you able to find Karin-dono?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.81,0:07:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Takamaru, there's something we need to talk about. Won't you come with me for a moment?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.78,0:07:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.15,0:07:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Takamaru, you're a precious friend to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.87,0:07:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to live my life distrusting you. {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.92,0:07:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So talk honestly.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.06,0:07:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't quite understand, \Nbut all right. {/but I understand - ???}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.24,0:07:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you doing last night?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.69,0:08:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Last night?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.21,0:08:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the Takamaru brat?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.67,0:08:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh. I'll show you something \Nfar more amusing in a moment.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.97,0:08:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Amusing?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.55,0:08:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.87,0:08:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what Karin-dono said?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.81,0:08:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I have no recollection of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.52,0:08:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Think harder, Takamaru.\NThis is a heavy problem!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.99,0:08:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened last night?\NTry to remember!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.74,0:08:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do you say? Surely, nothing \Nof the sort could have happened, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.89,0:08:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I say I don't remember a thing, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.16,0:08:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Takamaru!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.52,0:08:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.68,0:08:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Takamaru?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.74,0:08:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? \NIt's not time for sleep yet!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.46,0:09:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.33,0:09:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It can even do this.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.65,0:09:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takamaru, wake up!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.77,0:09:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,"Middle of conversation" \Nis not the time for sleeping!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.63,0:09:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you break out your \NMacho Technique all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.55,0:09:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Takamaru!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.23,0:09:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Takamaru!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.38,0:09:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, we need to keep a close eye \Non the area around The Smoking One...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.96,0:10:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What the... They're not supposed to operate without an order!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.26,0:10:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Gather up, people! Gather up! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.14,0:10:26.96,Thought,,0,0,0,,Takamaru is not the kind of guy \Nwho'd go around felling trees for no reason.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.96,0:10:28.70,Thought,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into him?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.19,0:10:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, only one more to take care of.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.20,0:10:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.48,0:10:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We made a bit of a blunder last night.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.31,0:10:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Who'd think that Mirai \Nwould prove that tough!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.60,0:10:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop! Takamaru, you need to stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.37,0:10:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me? \NI said, stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.80,0:10:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You stupid...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.39,0:10:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, Takamaru! \NSomething's terribly wrong with you!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.64,0:11:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Karin-san? Where have you been?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.79,0:11:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.69,0:11:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd save me a whole lot of trouble \Nif you just died then and there. {tema = trouble}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.63,0:11:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"Trouble?"
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.68,0:11:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about putting her \Nout of her misery, of course! {/dealing the finishing blow}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.28,0:11:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.78,0:11:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprised, aren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.13,0:11:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.43,0:11:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.22,0:11:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.17,0:11:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you— {?}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.11,0:11:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make this any more difficult, will you? {lit: don't deal me even more trouble (tema)}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.88,0:11:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you, really?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.62,0:11:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Takamaru, stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.02,0:11:49.19,Thought,,0,0,0,,Maybe Takamaru's caught \Na bad case of some brain disease?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.19,0:11:51.40,Thought,,0,0,0,,He's just like Alfred was the other day!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.34,0:11:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! He's heading straight for the Ninja Mansion!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.74,0:12:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I will... protect Mirai-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.93,0:12:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just quietly \Nwatch from there, Claude-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.20,0:12:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, as for you... {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.17,0:12:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end, Mirai!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.02,0:12:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{??}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.17,0:12:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You lowlife! {????????}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.49,0:12:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, what the... \NWhat are you clutching at?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.91,0:12:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of it, you hear?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.60,0:12:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.23,0:12:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You little pervert! \NLet go, you creep!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.00,0:12:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just about had enough of you!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.83,0:12:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Takamaru!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.30,0:12:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, my flute...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.54,0:12:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's my flute?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.68,0:12:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Karin, there you are!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.30,0:12:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not hurt, are you?\NTakamaru went completely off the rails.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.48,0:12:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It was so sudden Karin got scared!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.07,0:12:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Bullshit!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.51,0:13:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been leading everyone by the nose! \NKarin tried to kill Mirai-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.20,0:13:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.66,0:13:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would Karin want to kill Mirai?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.96,0:13:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know all the details, \Nbut it was Karin who injured Mirai-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.79,0:13:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Claude doesn't know what he's talking about. {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.11,0:13:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. \NSome people can be that annoying.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.55,0:13:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate it!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.51,0:13:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai ended up catching me red-handed. {lit: saw my plan}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.60,0:13:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to get rid of her. {lit: she became a nuisance}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.71,0:13:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys were too easy to fool.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.21,0:13:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Karin...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.12,0:13:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially Al—
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.18,0:13:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,all I had to do was act a little helpless, \Nand you fell for it at once. {burikko = woman or girl who acts cute by playing innocent and helpless​ - translated as "goody two-shoes" last time}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.56,0:13:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the laughs, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.98,0:13:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're joking, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.48,0:13:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that the Great Goblin Tarobo is sealed away,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.17,0:14:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Macho Man Takamaru will raze \Nthis Champon Kingdom to the ground!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.49,0:14:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Takamaru, \Ndeal with your best friend first!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.54,0:14:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Was Karin... Was Karin \Nmanipulating Takamaru all along?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.14,0:14:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Takamaru...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.02,0:14:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it? How does it feel \Nto be strangled by your best friend?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.82,0:14:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Karin, who are you really...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.43,0:14:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the top executive \Nof the Taiman army, Karin Fox.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.73,0:14:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Karin...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.91,0:14:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now die!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.37,0:14:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.87,0:14:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.21,0:14:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You obstinate pig!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.52,0:15:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Takamaru!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.94,0:15:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takamaru?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.76,0:15:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with them? {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.58,0:15:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? What's this?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.37,0:15:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugai-dono, did you find anything?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.50,0:15:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No, just some strange device \Nbehind their ears.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.30,0:15:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... That jerk Takamaru!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.25,0:15:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Karin! I can't believe you've been \Nfooling us all this time!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.14,0:15:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Karin, both Al Zaemon and Takamaru \Nthought of you as a friend.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.77,0:15:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.34,0:15:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter where you turn in this world, \Nall people do is scheme, lie, and backstab! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.16,0:16:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you even \Ncall yourself human?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.65,0:16:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans? Pft. \NDon't lump me in with them. {?}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.63,0:16:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a human.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.87,0:16:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can act any way I want, unbound \Nby stupid concepts such as emotions or morals.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.54,0:16:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it? \NDon't you think it's great?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.42,0:16:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.77,0:16:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.09,0:16:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's great about it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.32,0:16:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you pay, you monster! {/will never forgive you}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.49,0:16:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.19,0:16:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Takamaru?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.40,0:16:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever. I can get a new flute anytime.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.94,0:16:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Al! I'm looking forward \Nto seeing you "make me pay!" {/how you won't forgive me!}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.11,0:16:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Wait, you! Karin! \NAre you running away?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.04,0:16:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Al!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.70,0:16:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugai-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.51,0:16:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened? \NWhat's all the fuss?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.58,0:16:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.28,0:17:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, what happened is...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.28,0:17:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected—it's here.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.07,0:17:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It was highly unworthy of me. \NI was completely unprepared. {immature again}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.65,0:17:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve let myself be misled \Nby this device.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.20,0:17:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Takamaru, it’s not something \Nyou had a choice in. {?}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.18,0:17:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I’m sure they only succeeded \Nbecause my spirit wasn’t strong enough. {lit: because I had a gap in my heart}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.54,0:17:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I should’ve trained more.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.60,0:17:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Takamaru, let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.51,0:17:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll find Karin and kick her ass.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.73,0:17:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Al Zaemon.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.95,0:17:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I want you to do first.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.92,0:17:41.75,Thought,,0,0,0,,Damn this rogue Karin...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.67,0:17:44.16,Thought,,0,0,0,,Are you for real? {?}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.25,0:17:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If Mirai's map is to believed,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.48,0:17:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,there should be a stone on that island similar to one for sealing goblins.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.14,0:17:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So, is this the place?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.84,0:17:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Has to be it...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.37,0:18:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.67,0:18:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But which one?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.90,0:18:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How would we ever know \Nwhich hole to search?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.81,0:18:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.92,0:18:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Just search all of them, obviously!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.47,0:18:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s here! Ah, no.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.37,0:18:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Here! Here. Not, not here.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.60,0:18:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the one! No? No...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.61,0:18:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s here?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.23,0:18:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something in there.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.44,0:18:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Did you find it?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.23,0:18:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to reach it. {to feel around for; to fumble for; to grope for; to search for; to look for}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.51,0:18:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.34,0:18:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find the stone?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.07,0:18:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.59,0:18:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.28,0:18:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.07,0:18:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What could that be? \NIt has a sharp, hard tip...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.84,0:18:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharp tip?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.60,0:18:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And it’s turning!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.92,0:18:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Turning?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.03,0:18:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You...!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.90,0:18:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Drill Knight, the right hand of Karin Fox, \Nthe top executive of the Taiman Army!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.36,0:19:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you came to look for the goblin sealing stone, but I won’t let you have it!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.04,0:19:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,With my beautiful drill, \NI’ll send all of you six feet under!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.42,0:19:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.37,0:19:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Al, leave him to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.43,0:19:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to make it up to you for going rogue \Nwith my macho technique.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.65,0:19:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Drill Knight-dono, it is essential for us that the Great Goblin is restored to how he was.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.63,0:19:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you insist on stopping us no matter what, \NI’m going to be your opponent here. {?}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.79,0:19:31.77,Thought,,0,0,0,,That brat should still be under Karin’s control. {?}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.77,0:19:35.36,Thought,,0,0,0,,Well, why not? \NIt’ll look good on my service record. {lit: increase my achievement; feat; meritorious deed; distinguished service}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.76,0:19:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well! \NI’ll give you a taste of my beautiful drill! {???? nc what’s that tsuyu}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.55,0:19:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Champon Kingdom’s martial arts instructor, \Nson of Kibo Koen, Kibo Takamaru charges! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.72,0:19:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything but {\i1}that{\i0} technique!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.72,0:19:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So that’s how it is? {?}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.03,0:20:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't hurt my full-metal body!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.86,0:20:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If so...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.90,0:20:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Biting technique!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.44,0:20:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,H-H-He dented it!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.97,0:20:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My beautiful mechanical body...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.94,0:20:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My beautiful mechanical body!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.13,0:20:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And you dented it!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.38,0:20:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.59,0:20:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.42,0:20:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.66,0:20:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you can control my beautiful drill? \NThen how about this?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.36,0:20:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Takamaru!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.48,0:20:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You prick!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.16,0:20:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn’t it fun?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.58,0:21:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn brat!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.37,0:21:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Takamaru!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.38,0:21:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,For you, I have this!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.96,0:21:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my god!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.98,0:21:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My nice hair!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.06,0:21:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you’re getting it! Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.30,0:21:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.98,0:21:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll rid my boss of all three of you at once! {?}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.40,0:21:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro, your fan! {uchiwa; type of traditional Japanese handheld fan}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.82,0:21:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.20,0:21:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Your stupid tricks won’t help you!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.62,0:21:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:33.25,0:22:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Metals are quite difficult to grapple with.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:36.61,0:22:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for this instructive sparring!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:38.60,0:22:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You showed him, Takamaru!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:40.16,0:22:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive as ever!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:42.12,0:22:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m still learning.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:43.71,0:22:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's find the stone now.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:51.40,0:22:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Karin!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:53.23,0:22:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive for a bunch of snotty brats—\Nto beat Drill Knight himself.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:58.15,0:23:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I always knew this was the extent \Nof Drill Knight’s abilities.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:03.64,0:23:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Takamaru!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:05.99,0:23:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn Macho already!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:13.39,0:23:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting dancing style you have...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:16.25,0:23:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:18.67,0:23:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange... Why?!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:20.40,0:23:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ve long removed \Nall the chips you planted!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:26.36,0:23:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk. So you figured it out?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:28.87,0:23:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can’t defeat me \Nwith that kind of toy!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:31.95,0:23:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? Why don’t you dance for us \Nonce more, one final time, Karin?!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:43.65,0:23:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:47.16,0:23:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:50.60,0:23:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! We got her!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:52.65,0:23:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:24:01.22,0:24:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the last straw! \NNow you’ll definitely pay for this!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:10.57,0:24:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She’s running with her tail \Nbetween her legs.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:15.12,0:24:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I see now.\NKarin's weakness is frogs?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:19.57,0:24:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to approach \Nevery opponent individually! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:27.86,0:24:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Ouch, geez...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:31.51,0:24:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch where you’re going, you!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:33.41,0:24:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts! \NWhat's wrong with you, Karin?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:41.71,0:24:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Karin! Has something happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:44.07,0:24:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren’t you supposed to be \Nin the Champon Kingdom?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:48.22,0:24:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's the Undersea Fortress Jugon! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:51.36,0:24:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s on your mind, \Nbringing something like this out?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:54.16,0:24:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll sink Champon \Nto the bottom of the sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:58.06,0:25:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say? \NNo way, Karin! You have to stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:00.88,0:25:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Taiman-sama clearly ordered us to conquer \NChampon Kingdom—not destroy it!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:07.80,0:25:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The people of that kingdom are too dangerous—\Nwe must destroy them before it’s too late!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:13.83,0:25:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How can that micro-nation \Nbe {\i1}so{\i0} dangerous?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:17.89,0:25:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you should know it better than anyone, \Nwhat their children are capable of.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:23.96,0:25:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Even as enemies, I can’t help but admire \NTakamaru, Al, and Mirai.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:28.99,0:25:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,In ten years’ time, those kids will be completely immune to these cheap tricks. {?}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:38.26,0:25:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You nip the danger in the bud—\Nwhile it’s still defenseless!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:43.65,0:25:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Course Z built. {?}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:45.74,0:25:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Undersea Fortress Jugon surfaces. {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:23.64,0:28:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They want to send our homeland \Nof Champon to the bottom of the sea!
